cat << EOF
Makagiga is a powerful, easy-to-use, cross-platform application for doing a
variety of tasks, such as text editing, todo listing, and simple image editing.
Plugins are used to implement is various capabilities. It can perform file
import/export, backing up files into a zip file, Internet searching (Google,
Wikipedia), and more. The interface features custom colors, a tabbed view, and
labels and comments for each file or folder.
